{"tid":2263583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高志森：一哥演技比當年進步","createTime":"2020-10-30T04:05:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-14T13:02:29.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7ad7e410ebdef7c02924f36b069d3914003d4919","tid":2263583,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T04:05:36.000Z","msg":"警方噚日推出新片，宣傳藝人鍾鎮濤（阿B）嘅撐警歌曲《捍衛香港》，警務處長鄧炳強更粉墨登場。短片講述一名警員喺電梯偶遇一哥，一哥問對方聽緊咩歌，點解只係得10秒長，警員回應話足本版噚晚先喺電視台首播。一哥大讚歌詞有意義，最後仲唱咗幾句《捍衛香港》。一哥讀大學時曾客串高志森首次執導嘅電影《開心鬼》，與同學一齊拍戲掙錢；高志森噚日睇完條片就喺facebook稱讚一哥演技比當年進步。<br />\n<br />\n另外，由香港電台同警察公共關係科（PPRB）聯合製作嘅節目《警訊》，喺8月結束長達47年嘅製作，新節目《警聲直播》噚晚喺警隊facebook專頁同YouTube頻道首播，其中一名主持係10月獲頒銅英勇勳章嘅高級督察黃家倫。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/港聞/article/20201030/s00002/1603995782554/【emily】鄧炳強客串撐警歌mv-獲讚演技進步\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20201030%2Fs00002%2F1603995782554%2F%E3%80%90emily%E3%80%91%E9%84%A7%E7%82%B3%E5%BC%B7%E5%AE%A2%E4%B8%B2%E6%92%90%E8%AD%A6%E6%AD%8Cmv-%E7%8D%B2%E8%AE%9A%E6%BC%94%E6%8A%80%E9%80%B2%E6%AD%A5&d=L3LYojiCq%2FWCCnzMgLa5KMbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=d43d09f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20201030%2Fs00002%2F1603995782554%2F%E3%80%90emily%E3%80%91%E9%84%A7%E7%82%B3%E5%BC%B7%E5%AE%A2%E4%B8%B2%E6%92%90%E8%AD%A6%E6%AD%8Cmv-%E7%8D%B2%E8%AE%9A%E6%BC%94%E6%8A%80%E9%80%B2%E6%AD%A5&h=d242e65b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/港聞/article/20201030/s00002/1603995782554/【emily】鄧炳強客串撐警歌mv-獲讚演技進步</a>"},{"pid":"9a79c6a2bf051460cb4fd34be200bc5d18a588d5","tid":2263583,"uid":11291,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T04:08:03.000Z","msg":"咪又係小丑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c068ec1d549ee4a7c3697735eabd79ff75179d44","tid":2263583,"uid":143499,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T04:09:23.0